The paper discusses machine learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and often involves large datasets (cs.DS). The paper also discusses security and privacy concerns (cs.CR) in the context of multi-party machine learning (cs.SI). Finally, the paper proposes a method for defending against attacks (adversarial training), which is a common technique in the field of deep learning (cs.LG).
